<taxonomicName authority="Marshall, 2019" authorityName="Marshall" authorityYear="2019" box="[297,511,1876,1901]" class="Insecta" family="Micropezidae" genus="Mesoconius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zorro" status="sp. nov.">
