<emphasis bold="true" box="[874,895,1875,1901]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96">A</emphasis>
. Spermathecae and associated structures. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,209,1911,1937]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96">B</emphasis>
. Male abdomen, left side. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[514,535,1911,1937]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96">C</emphasis>
